title: Blobmixer
description: The Blobmixer is a toy for creating 3D art; own it as a video, view it in VR, or share it with friends. In total, 1414 pieces will be minted and become part of our NFT collection, whose profits will be donated to charity via The Giving Block. The Blobmixer was born with the 14islands brand as an abstraction of islands surrounded by water. Blobs are never perfectly round and always changing shapes, like islands that change with tides and waves.
